text: Renuka Bishnoi (born 1 September 1973) is an Indian politician from Indian National Congress and a member of the Haryana Legislative Assembly. She was elected from Hansi in October 2014 on a Haryana Janhit Congress ticket. ==Personal life== She is married to Kuldeep Bishnoi and has 3 children, Bhavya Bishnoi, Chaitanya Bishnoi and Sia Bishnoi. ==References== Category:Haryana MLAs 2014–2019 Category:Women in Haryana politics Category:Living people Category:1973 births Category:Members of the Haryana Legislative Assembly Category:Haryana Janhit Congress politicians Category:21st-century Indian women politicians Category:21st-century Indian politicians
title: Renuka Bishnoi
